///
///   Parse-time lexical scope stack. Tracks locals, generic parameters in
///   scope, and captured names during parsing. Distinct from HoistedScope
///   (which is indexer-built, file-global, and read-only during parse).
///
///   Part of the Kairo Project, under the Apache License v2.0 with the
///   Kairo Runtime Library Exception.
